<p class="ql-align-center">火把节假期来了，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还在愁该怎么玩？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没关系，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这份火把节攻略请接住！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">到凉山打卡美景、</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">品尝美食，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把各县市特色伴手礼带回家！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 蠢蠢欲动了有没有？？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让我们一起出发去凉山，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">走起！</p>
